location.physicalLocation: British Library: India Office Records and Private Papers

physicalDescription.extent: Materials: Printed in colour on paper.Dimensions: 300 x 207mm, on sheet 328 x 251mm.

mods.abstract: Plan of the port of Jedda. The plan indicates hydrology and settlements, and provides some indication of relief.Includes the following printing statement: 'Produced under the Superintendence of Rear-Admiral J.A. Edgell, C.B., O.B.E., Hydrographer.' Prepared by naval staff in the Admiralty's Naval Intelligence Division.
